directions: Preheat oven to 350 degrees F (175 degrees C). Grease a 9x13 inch pan. Put a single layer of miniature marshmallows on the bottom of the pan.
Prepare cake mix according to package instructions. Pour batter over marshmallows in pan.
Mix gelatin powder and strawberries in a medium bowl. Pour over cake batter in the pan.
ingredients: 1 (6 ounce) package orange flavored Jell-O® mix
title: Strawberry Upside Down Cake
